# removeEntry(at:)

**Instance Method**

Removes and releases the entry at the specified index.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor func removeEntry(at index: Int)
```

## Parameters

- **index**: The zero-based index identifying the desired entry.

## Discussion

If the specified index is invalid, this method does nothing.

## Adding and Removing Entries

- **addEntry(_:)**: Adds a new entry to the end of the receiver and gives it the specified title.
- **insertEntry(_:at:)**: Inserts an entry with the specified title into the receiver.
